title: Colts' fake punt among NFL's dumbest plays
text: > Top News Colts' fake punt among NFL's dumbest plays FILE - In this Nov. 25, 1993, file photo, Dallas Cowboys' Leon Lett (78) and Miami Dolphins' Bert Weidner (60) reach for a ball after Lett slides into the ball after the Cowboys blocked a field goal attempt in the snow during an NFL game in Irving, Texas. After Lett touched the ball the Dolphins recovered and then kicked again for the win. The Dolphins won 16-14. (Star-Telegram via AP) MAGS OUT; (FORT WORTH WEEKLY, 360 WEST); INTERNET OUT; MANDATORY CREDIT
